Sigma Rules
-----------

- Sigma rules are written in YAML and are used to detect malicious behaviour; usually within a SIEM platform

* https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma

* https://pypi.org/project/sigmatools/0.17.0/

* https://socprime.com/blog/sigma-rules-the-beginners-guide/

* https://www.picussecurity.com/resource/glossary/what-is-sigma-rule

* https://www.csoonline.com/article/572973/sigma-rules-explained-when-and-how-to-use-them-to-log-events.html

* https://sigmahq.io/docs/basics/rules.html
